== Mu Rwanda ==
Ubutegetsi bw'ingoma ya cyami mu Rwanda rwo hambere bwari bushingiye k'umwami ariwe nyir'igihugu ariko bukagenda bugira izindi nzego cyangwa abandi bantu batandukanye bagendaga bafasha cyangwa se bunganiraga Umwami uri ku ngomba mu buryo butandukanye.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Archive copy |url=https://umusare.co.rw/isomero/amateka-yu-rwanda-ibyo-wamenya-ku-itorwa-numumaro-wabagabekazi-mu-butegetsi-bwa-cyami |accessdate=2020-10-13 |archive-date=2020-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013194659/https://umusare.co.rw/isomero/amateka-yu-rwanda-ibyo-wamenya-ku-itorwa-numumaro-wabagabekazi-mu-butegetsi-bwa-cyami |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 

Amatwara y'Ingoma-Ngabe aboneka mu bwiru; yavugaga ko iyo umwami yimaga, yimanaga na nyina, umwana akaba umwami w'igihugu, undi akaba umugabekazi wacyo, Umugabekazi akaba yaranganyaga ububasha n'Umwami. ibyemezo byose biyobora igihugu bakabifatira hamwe, ariko nanone nubwo amahame ya cyami yavugaga ko abagore bose ari ab'Umwami, ntibishaka kuvugako umugore w'Umwami wese umugabekazi. Umwami yagiraga Umwamikazi umwe, abandi bakaba inshoreke. bityo rero umwamikazi yagiraga aho akomoka akaba ari nawe uzaba umugabekazi, agategekana n'umuhungu we igihe Umwami yabaga [http://www.wikirwanda.org/index.php?title=Ikeshamvugo yatanze.]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Archive copy |url=https://umusare.co.rw/isomero/amateka-yu-rwanda-ibyo-wamenya-ku-itorwa-numumaro-wabagabekazi-mu-butegetsi-bwa-cyami |accessdate=2020-10-13 |archive-date=2020-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013194659/https://umusare.co.rw/isomero/amateka-yu-rwanda-ibyo-wamenya-ku-itorwa-numumaro-wabagabekazi-mu-butegetsi-bwa-cyami |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
