== Umumaro w'Umugabekazi ==
Umugabekazi yabaga afite ububasha mu gufata ibyemezo, ubwo bubasha yabugiraga nyuma yuko umuhungu we yimye Ingoma akaba umwami. kuko mugihe yabaga ari Umwamikazi yaherekezaga umwami mu birori cyangwa mu butumire butandukanye ari ntabyemezo ashobora kugiramo uruhare kugeza Umwami atanze umuhungu we akima Ingoma.<ref>http://igicumbi.com/index.php/amateka/ibwami/item/571-rwanda-ibintu-20-wamenya-ku-mwamikazi-rosalie-gicanda</ref>

